name: Menenti 2014
description:
PRE ORDER NOW, for your chance to win an exclusive Signed photograph of Duncan James from boy band BLUE! 

MéNENTI 2014 is available from November 5th 2013, featuring Blue's Duncan James with a 10 page cover spread of Brand New never before seen beautiful and sexy photos. Following last years issue we are also showcasing some of the fashion industries best new faces of the year, and some new music industry guys too. 120 pages of some of London's most handsome new talent, beautifully shot to the highest quality by photographer Joe McCormick.

In this issue you will find lots of new faces, aswell as a few follow up shoots and interviews from some of last years favourites! 

Pre orders will be delivered between November 5th & 7th 2013.

name: Faces of 2013 Issue #1
description:
MéNENTI: The Faces Of 2013 is available in one of  two covers, featuring either Freddie Ransom or Primo Baker, showcasing some of the fashion industries best new faces of the year with 120 pages of some of London's most handsome new models, beautifully shot to the highest quality by photographer Joe McCormick.

Other featured models include:

Tyler Sheekey
William Payne
Ryan Darvill
Charlie Mills
Nick Gibbens
Louis Berry
Sam Mellen
Boyd Alves
and many more...
